{"tid":2290182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「裝修」兼夾疫情　美心伍氏家族公司減派息　伍淑清少袋70萬元　第4代獲分股份","createTime":"2020-11-17T23:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T06:14:42.000Z","uid":271829,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0eacae6f230b4f3b52a99509a74722cf5544c3","tid":2290182,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T23:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a9JX-6WJGxRZswr_MB4hEHGUvf8=/819x423/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YYTIJR24O5BRVKKOFTF52MPYSA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa9JX-6WJGxRZswr_MB4hEHGUvf8%3D%2F819x423%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYYTIJR24O5BRVKKOFTF52MPYSA.jpg&h=62a32b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n去年逆權運動下，美心集團創辦人伍沾德長女伍淑清不斷抨擊示威的年輕人，導致旗下飲食品牌慘遭杯葛及「裝修」，加上在年初武漢肺炎事件下，業績更大倒退。本報翻查持有美心50%股份的伍氏家族企業香港食品有限公司（Hong Kong Caterers，簡稱香港食品）截至今年3月底止最新財報，披露美心貢獻盈利減逾2成至6.4億元，導致股東之一伍淑清少收股息70萬元，但仍獲得387.2萬元。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201117/NVEZV3KBP5BBZPTZ2BKAYONPQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201117%2FNVEZV3KBP5BBZPTZ2BKAYONPQQ%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1edgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=2d690f05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201117%2FNVEZV3KBP5BBZPTZ2BKAYONPQQ%2F&h=780788c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201117/NVEZV3KBP5BBZPTZ2BKAYONPQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"cdb7af36672ebe2b3e1abf770c80e5b6e136ec0d","tid":2290182,"uid":185631,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T23:53:44.000Z","msg":"唔駛做仲有成300萬股息收<br />\n多謝藍絲支持啦！"},{"pid":"a210c959aba9d178c47fc21c4f1155858d697bf1","tid":2290182,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T23:57:09.000Z","msg":"放棄兩代人都仲有400萬袋"},{"pid":"1